Record Class Cell

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
fr.connexe.algo.Cell
Record Components:
pos - the position of the cell within the maze, starting at (0, 0).
wallLeft - indicates if the cell has a wall to the left.
wallRight - indicates if the cell has a wall to the right.
wallUp - indicates if the cell has a wall above.
wallDown - indicates if the cell has a wall below.
endpoint - indicates if this cell is a start or end cell.
public record Cell(Point pos, boolean wallLeft, boolean wallRight, boolean wallUp, boolean wallDown, Cell.Endpoint endpoint) extends Record

A cell located within an ArrayMaze.

Cells indicate their boundaries: walls present in either direction (left/right, up/down).
